      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Matlock ¶ Vic. ¶ , 30 January 1869 ¶ Dear Father! ¶  ¶ […] ¶ Passages unrelated to M omitted. ¶  ¶  ¶ So far I am still quite well, but I have decided to ¶  ¶ accept ¶  ¶ a position with Dr Mueller in...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">M69.01.30</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Georg Luehmann to Johann Christian<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Luehmann</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Private hands.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">Matlock, 30 Januar 1869</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Lieber Vater!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">[</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">…</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">]</seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Passages unrelated to M omitted.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mir geht es so weit noch ganz gut, ich habe mich aber entschlossen, in etwa einem Monate eine Stelle bei Dr Mueller in Melbourne anzunehmen. Obgleich das Goldgraben eine sehr angenehme, wenn auch schwierige Beschäftigung ist, welche mir für die<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Gegenwart recht wohl gefällt, so komme ich dabei doch nicht viel weiter, da ich leider sagen muss, dass ich wie alle andern Goldsucher zu verschwenderisch geworden bin. Ich werde in Melbourne für den Anfang freilich nicht so viel verdienen (6 shilling oder 2<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>rth den Tag nebst freier Wohnung und Feuerholze, muss mich aber selbst beköstigen).<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Da es aber eine Regierungs Anstellung ist, so habe ich Aussicht mich zu verbessern, wenn mir nur die Lebensweise nach dem freien unabhängigen Leben auf den Goldfeldern zusagen wird.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Ich habe neben etwas Gold zu Hause, jetzt 150 Pfund in der Bank; wenn es auch nicht so viel ist, wie es hätte sein sollen, so hat mancher doch weiniges erübrigt.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[…]</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Dein</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>gehorsamer Sohn</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>J. G. Lühmann</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Matlock<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Vic.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>, 30 January 1869</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Dear Father!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[…]<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Passages unrelated to M omitted.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>So far I am still quite well, but I have decided to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>accept<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>a position with Dr Mueller in Melbourne in about a month. Although gold digging is a very pleasant occupation, even if a difficult one,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>pleases me quite well for the present, yet<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I am not getting much further on<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>with it, because unfortunately I must say that I, like all other gold seekers, have been too wasteful. Admittedly at the start in Melbourne I will not earn so much (6 shillings or 2 reichtalers per day with free housing and firewood, but must cater for myself). However, as it is a government appointment, I have the prospect to improve myself, if only the way of life will suit me after the free independent life on the gold fields. Besides some gold at home, I have now 150 pounds in the bank, even if not so much as it should have been, many a one has indeed saved less.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[…]</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Your dutiful son</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>J. G. Lühmann</p>
         </div>
